                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5.1">
                     <locus from="108va" to="111vb"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT3183Commen#Hosea">Interpretation of the kings' names mentioned in Hosea</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">ፍካሬ፡ ነገሥተ፡ ይሁዳ፡ ዘከሮሙ፡ ነቢይ፡ ዘነ</hi>ግሡ፡ በ፩ጊዜ፡ እለ፡ እንዘ፡ ይተለዉ፨  
